Special Forces ground raid

13:40.553 --> 13:42.822 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in the country.

13:42.855 --> 13:45.024 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
The Pentagon said at the time

13:45.057 --> 13:46.859 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
