13:51.997 --> 13:54.133 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
>> AHMAD: The raid took place on
a tiny little village

13:54.166 --> 13:58.571 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
called Athlan on May 23, 2017.

13:58.604 --> 14:00.039 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The people who lived in the
village described

14:00.072 --> 14:03.342 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
