they were so frightened

14:03.375 --> 14:07.079 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
about the amount of U.S.
soldiers that were sent.

14:07.112 --> 14:11.417 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
There were the helicopters,
the drones.

14:11.450 --> 14:14.353 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
>> NARRATOR: The villagers say
Safa is the first

14:14.386 --> 14:19.291 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
foreign journalist to come here
since the U.S. raid.

