14:30.769 --> 14:33.205 align:left position:12.5%,start line:0% size:87.5%
AHMAD and MUJAHID:

14:40.679 --> 14:43.215 align:left position:37.5%,start line:0% size:62.5%
CHILD:

14:51.257 --> 14:52.091 align:left position:0%,start line:0% size:100%
(Abu Mo'ath speaking Arabic)

14:52.124 --> 14:53.559 align:left position:37.5%,start line:0% size:62.5%
CHILD:

14:55.794 --> 14:57.229 align:left position:37.5%,start line:0% size:62.5%
MO'ATH:

14:57.863 --> 14:59.298 align:left position:37.5%,start line:0% size:62.5%
CHILD:

