the U.S. attacked their village

18:27.172 --> 18:29.174 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
two years ago.

18:29.208 --> 18:30.742 align:left position:37.5%,start line:0% size:62.5%
SINAN:

18:35.614 --> 18:38.851 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
>> AHMAD: The Yemenis I've spoke
to in Yakla and Athlan

18:38.884 --> 18:42.621 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
